<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="4200">13.2. Template variables</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Template variables are pre-defined variables that can be inserted in email templates. When sending the emails, this variable is automatically filled with the corresponding content. Template variables start with a dollar sign (<code>$</code>) followed by an upper-case character. <a href="#table-template-variables-emails">Table 9</a> lists the template variables that are available for email templates.</p>
</div>
