<div class="title">Template variable logic</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Note that template variables can only be filled with content when certain requirements are met.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Examples:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>$TicketLastMessage</code> is only filled with content when an event procedure was set up that reacts to a new ticket message</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>$OrderId</code> is only filled and sent in combination with orders. For example, if the "Forgot password" function is used, the system would not know which order ID to use because the reference to an order is missing.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
